3211640%2Fwhy-hermes-birkin-bag-such-good-investment-according-experts-other-luxury-handbags-might-not-be%5C%22%3Eeven%20outperforming%20traditional%20asset%20classes%20such%20as%20gold%20and%20stocks%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mother%20scoffed%20at%20the%20idea.%20Growing%20up%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20we%20didn't%20see%20many%20Birkins%20in%20person.%20This%20was%20a%20bag%20for%20the%20glossies%20%E2%80%94%20not%20an%20item%20to%20be%20listed%20in%20a%20wealth%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20my%20career%20as%20a%20business%20reporter%20has%20had%20me%20reporting%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiggest-luxury-buyers-gen-y-z-alpha-2023-2%5C%22%3Estories%20about%20luxury%20items%20as%20investments%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0I%20was%20jolted%20back%20to%20this%20particular%20conversation%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fjane-birkin-dead-at-76-life-in-photos-2023-7%5C%22%3Ereading%20Jane%20Birkin's%20obituary%20over%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%2C%20for%20me%2C%20the%20Birkin%20bag%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bagover.com%2Fhermes-birkin-bag-price-list%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Cost%253A%2520Birkin%2520Bag%2520Price%26amp%3Btext%3DThe%2520more%2520attainable%2520Birkins%252C%2520cheapest%2Cthe%2520more%2520high%252Dend%2520designs.%5C%22%3Ewhich%20retails%20for%20anywhere%20from%20%2410%2C000%20to%20%24250%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dbb4084d5d5328ee27a9835bea3fd63351816d019624c45747912e72824f1461c%26postID%3D64b4d42e422826601a574303%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.sothebys.com%252Fen%252Farticles%252Fthe-top-6-most-expensive-hermes-birkin-bags%5C%22%3Ehigh-end%20designs%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20primarily%20represents%20a%20store%20of%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%2C%20for%20example%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.deloitte.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2FDeloitte%2Fch%2FDocume