n%20Patna%20in%20June.%20The%20opposition%20has%20jeered%20that%20its%20unity%20move%20--%20modelled%20after%20the%20JP%20movement%20of%201970s%20--%20has%20had%20the%20BJP%20jarred.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20though%2C%20has%20been%20moving%20in%20a%20planned%20manner.%20Most%20of%20its%20push%20has%20been%20in%20Bihar%2C%20where%20Nitish%20Kumar%20had%20mopped%20up%20the%20board%20when%20he%20parted%20company%20with%20the%20NDA%2C%20leaving%20only%20the%20fractured%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20to%20the%20BJP.%20The%20BJP%20is%20now%20attempting%20to%20effect%20a%20reconciliation%20between%20Chirag%20Paswan%20and%20its%20uncle%2C%20which%20will%20give%20it%20access%20to%20the%20six%20per%20cent%20Paswan%20votes.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20more%20parties%20from%20Bihar%20--%20Upendra%20Singh%20Kushwaha%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Samta%20Party%2C%20and%20Mukesh%20Sahani%20of%20the%20Vikassheel%20Insaan%20Party%20and%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%20of%20Hindustani%20Awam%20Morcha%20--%20are%20expected%20to%20join%20the%20NDA.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20mammoth%2080-seat%20state%20where%20the%20BJP%20is%20already%20extremely%20strong%2C%20the%20party%20has%20added%20one%20more%20ally%20--%20the%20Suheldev%20Bhartiya%20Samaj%20Party%20of%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%20--%20with%20what%20many%20feel%20is%20the%20hope%20to%20offset%20the%20losses%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20key%20allies%20-%20AIADMK%20and%20Tamil%20Manila%20Congress%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Eknath%20Shinde%20faction)%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20NCP%20in%20Maharashtra%20--are%20expected%20to%20keep%20the%20seat%20count%20up%20in%20the%20two%20major%20states%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20also%20kept%20close%20its%20allies%20in%20the%20northeast.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeven%20parties%20that%20helps%20the%20BJP%20govern%20the%20seven%20northeastern%20states%20--%20NPP%20(National%20People's%20Party%20Meghalaya)%2C%20NDPP%20(Nationalist%20Democratic%20Progressive%20Party)%2C%20SKM%20(Sikkim%20Krantikari%20Morcha)%2C%20MNF%20(Mizo%20National%20Front)%2C%20ITFT%20(Tripura)%2C%20BPP%20(Bodo%20People's%20party)%20and%20AGP%20(Asom%20Gana%20Parishad)%20--%20are%20on%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20few%20new%20entrants%20also.%20Besides%20the%20ones%20in%20Bihar%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20drawn%20actor%20Pawan%20Kalyan's%20Jansena%20and%20the%20faction%20of%20Kerala%20Congress%20led%20by%20Kerala%20Congress%20(Thomas).%20The%20latter%20had%20quit%20the%20NDA%20in%202021%20alleging%20trouble%20in%20seat%20sharing%2C%20but%20has%20since%20refreshed%20the%20alliance.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20overall%20makes%20clear%20the%20party's%20trajectory.%20Already%20strong%20in%20most%20northern%20states%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20sticking%20to%20its%20plan%20of%20beefing%20up%20in%20the%20south%2C%20west%20and%20northeast.%20In%20crucial%20states%20like%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Bihar%2C%20it%20is%20only%20seeking%20to%20extend%20its%20footprint%20by%20patching%20in%20parties%20that%20have%20influence%20among%20backward%20classes%20and%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Tribes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689602340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fcrh9p0t_jp-nadda-_625x300_30_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F38-parties-will-attend-nda-meeting-tomorrow-says-bjp-chief-jp-nadda-4215308%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20today%20confirmed%20that%2038%20parties%20will%20attend%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20or%20NDA%20meet%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20in%20what%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20mega%20show%20of%20strength.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F38-parties-will-attend-nda-meeting-tomorrow-says-bjp-chief-jp-nadda-4215308%22%2C%22cdnAmpUr