-2023-7%5C%22%3Esold%20the%20heiress%20and%20his%20other%20rich%20friends%20fake%20Birkins.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThings%20began%20to%20unravel%20when%20he%20sold%20someone%20a%20%26quot%3Bobvious%2C%20slouching%2C%20laughably%20low-quality%20fake.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBut%20the%20first%20red%20flag%20should%20have%20been%20a%20forged%20Herm%C3%A8s%20receipt%20that%20featured%20the%20wrong%20font.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20social%20climber%20with%20fabulous%20hair%20has%20been%20booted%20from%20New%20York%20high%20society%20after%20selling%20socialites%20fake%20Herm%C3%A8s%20bags.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20week%2C%20Insider%20published%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeorge-mickum-gillian-hearst-hermes-birkin-society-scam-2023-7%5C%22%3Ea%20deep%20dive%20into%20George%20Mickum%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Gillian%20Hearst's%20former%20best%20friend%20who%20sold%20the%20media%20heiress%20and%20his%20other%20wealthy%20friends%20knock-off%20Birkins.%20Mickum's%20downfall%20began%20in%202022%20when%20he%20promised%20to%20buy%20a%20fashion%20executive%20a%2040-centimeter%20version%20of%20Herm%C3%A8s'%20rare%20Haut%20%C3%A0%20Courroies%20Birkin%2C%20or%20HAC%2C%20in%20khaki%20green.%20The%20executive%2C%20who%20was%20dating%20one%20of%20Mickum's%20close%20friends%2C%20knew%20it%20would%20be%20nearly%20impossible%20to%20find%20the%20recently-released%20bag%20in%20stores.%20He%20thought%20working%20with%20Mickum%20could%20save%20him%20significant%20time%20and%20money.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Mickum%20made%20several%20missteps.%20First%2C%20in%20April%202022%2C%20he%20sent%20the%20executive%20a%20photo%20of%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20receipt%20from%20the%20Herm%C3%A8s%20store%20in%20Paris.%20According%20to%20the%20receipt%2C%20Mickum%20had%20bought%20the%20HAC%20for%2019%2C200%20euros%2C%20or%20about%20%2421%2C000.%20It%20looked%20legitimate%3A%20the%20receipt%20featured%20the%20address%20of%20the%20brand's%20flagship%20on%20Rue%20du%20Faubourg%20Saint-Honor%C3%A9%2C%20a%20purchase%20date%20of%20March%2012%2C%20and%20even%20a%20pale%20yellow%20Herm%C3%A8s%20watermark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20Alexis%20Clarbour%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20sales%20at%20the%20luxury-bag%20reseller%20Madison%20Avenue%20Couture%2C%20saw%20the%20receipt%20months%20later%20she%20immediately%20knew%20it%20was%20fake.%20There%20were%20countless%20errors%2C%20Clarbour%20told%20Insider%20%E2%80%94%20even%20the%20font%20was%20wrong.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMickum's%20next%20misstep%20came%20when%20he%20delivered%20the%20bag%20to%20the%20executive.%20Instead%20of%20a%20signature%20orange%20Herm%C3%A8s%20box%2C%20he%20stuffed%20it%20into%20a%20Bergdorf%20Goodman%20bag.%20It%20was%20as%20if%20Mickum%20had%20found%20%26quot%3Ban%20old%20Nike%20gym%20bag%26quot%3B%20and%20dumped%20it%20into%20the%20shopping%20bag%2C%20the%20executive%20said.%20There%20wasn't%20even%20a%20dust%20bag%3B%20Mickum%20claimed%20his%20mom's%20assistant%20would%20drop%20it%20off%20later.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20there%20was%20the%20bag%20itself.%20As%20soon%20as%20he%20saw%20the%20HAC%2C%20the%20executive%20knew%20Mickum%20was%20trying%20to%20sell%20him%20a%20fake%20bag%20%E2%80%94%20an%20%26quot%3Bobvious%2C%20slouching%2C%20laughably%20low-quality%20fake%26quot%3B%20at%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20executive%20and%20his%20girlfriend%20brought%20the%20HAC%20to%20Clarbour%2C%20she%20immediately%20clocked%20several%20issues.%20It%20was%20floppy%2C%20like%20a%20bouncy%20castle%20that%20had%20lost%20half%20its%20air%2C%20instead%20of%20having%20the%20architectural%20stiffness%20of%20a%20real%20Herm%C3%A8s%20bag.%20There%20was%20no%20date%20stamp%20indicating%20when%20the%20bag%20was%20produced%20and%20no%20craft%20stamp%20denoting%20the%20artisan%20who'd%20produced%20it.%20Clarbour%20didn't%20even%20think%20the%20bag%20had%20been%20produced%20yet%20at%20the%20time%20when%20Mickum%20claimed%20to%20have%20had%20bought%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20HAC%20was%20one%20of%20at%20least%20six%20fake%20Herm%C3%A8s%20bags%20Mickum%20had%20sold%20to%20friends%2C%20including%20Hearst.%20Mickum%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%20A%20lawyer%20for%20Hearst%2C%20his%20friend-turned-nemesis%2C%20said%20of%20our%20investigation%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20assert%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20this%20information%20is%20not%20only%20erroneous%20but%20grossly%20misleading.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fkate-taylor%5C%22%3ERead%20the%20full%20saga%20of%20the%20fake%20Birkins%20here.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-the-scammer-selling-nyc-socialites-fake-birkins-got-caught-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689601906000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ad65178ed31300199e6ced%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-the-scammer-selling-nyc-socialites-fake-birkins-got-caught-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20forged%20Herm%C3%A8s%20receipt%2C%20poor%20craftsmanship%20and%20random%20Bergdorf%20Goodman%20bag%20were%20some%20of%20the%20tell-tale%20signs%20George%20Mickum's%20Birkins%20were%20fake.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktaylor%40businessinsider.com%20(Kate%20Taylor%2CAnna%20Silman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-the-scammer-selling-nyc-socialites-fake-birkins-got-caught-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tunisia-EU%20migration%3A%20Deal%20signed%20to%20strengthen%20borders%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689601768000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F10568%2Fproduction%2F_130402966_gettyimages-1497232252.