noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffsinsight.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFundstrat's%3C%2Fa%3E%20Tom%20Lee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20tailwind%20is%20a%20weakening%20US%20dollar%2C%20which%20according%20to%20a%20Monday%20note%20from%20Lee%2C%20should%20help%20lift%20profit%20margins%20for%20US%20multinational%20companies%20over%20the%20next%20two%20to%20three%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20falling%20dollar%20helps%20US%20companies%20because%20when%20they%20sell%20their%20products%20overseas%2C%20they%20receive%20foreign%20currencies%20and%20convert%20them%20into%20dollars.%20A%20weak%20dollar%2C%20in%20tandem%20with%20stronger%20foreign%20currencies%2C%20means%20they%20receive%20more%20dollars%20when%20they%20convert%20their%20foreign%20currencies%2C%20ultimately%20helping%20boost%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Dollar%20Index%2C%20which%20measures%20the%20dollar%20against%20a%20basket%20of%20foreign%20currencies%2C%20has%20declined%20by%2013%25%20from%20its%20September%20high%20of%20about%20115%20to%20just%20under%20100%20today.%20The%20decline%20represents%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fus-dollar-breakdown-usd-currency-euro-breakout-forex-technical-analysis-2023-7%5C%22%3Ea%20breakdown%20in%20the%20dollar%20below%20a%20key%20support%20level%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20according%20to%20a%20recent%20note%20from%20Fairlead%20Strategies%2C%20suggesting%20that%20the%20weakness%20could%20persist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRecall%2C%20the%20surge%20in%20%5Bthe%5D%20US%20dollar%20in%202022%20subtracted%205%25%20to%207%25%20from%20EPS%20results%2C%20so%20this%20payback%20should%20boost%20results%20for%20the%20next%20two%20to%20three%20quarters%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20second-quarter%20results%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20the%20worst%20quarter%20for%20year-over-year%20comparisons%2C%20based%20on%20current%20Wall%20Street%20estimates%2C%20they%20should%20represent%20the%20bottom%20and%20rebound%20in%20the%20third%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20overall%20takeaway%20is%20that%20earnings%20comparisons%20will%20start%20to%20get%20easier%20in%20the%20next%20few%20quarters%20due%20to%20weaker%20US%20dollar%2C%20easier%20year%20ago%20EPS%20and%20stabilizing%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sectors%20that%20should%20see%20the%20biggest%20lift%20in%20earnings%20due%20to%20the%20weakening%20dollar%20are%20industrials%20and%20technology%2C%20which%20both%20have%20plenty%20of%20overseas%20exposure%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20Lee%20expects%20earnings%20to%20surprise%20to%20the%20upside%2C%20in%20part%20driven%20by%20the%20weaker%20dollar%2C%20and%20that%20should%20help%20lift%20the%20stock%20market%20to%20record%20highs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20all-time%20highs%20are%20really%20the%20next%20target%20for%20the%20market%20broadly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22862%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Falling%20US%20dollar%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b541e1dcdf1100194c26c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22678%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EFundstrat%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-2nd-half-gains-falling-us-dollar-tailwind-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689601661000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f45218a42f43f001ddfed59%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-2nd-half-gains-falling-us-dollar-tailwind-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20two%20sectors%20that%20should%20see%20the%20biggest%20lift%20in%20earnings%20due%20to%20the%20weakening%20US%20dollar%20are%20industrials%20and%20technology%2C%20accordi