01981.%3Cp%3EReg%20Burkett%2FGettyImages%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJane%20Birkin%2C%20the%20inspiration%20behind%20the%20iconic%20Birkin%20bag%2C%20died%20inside%20her%20Paris%20home%20on%20Sunday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20bag%20is%20a%20status%20symbol%20and%20fetches%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20on%20the%20resale%20market.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBirkin%20revealed%20the%20origin%20story%20of%20the%20handbag%20to%20a%20Vogue%20contributor%20in%202012.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20iconic%20Herm%C3%A9s%20Birkin%20handbag%2C%20which%20is%20named%20after%20the%20late%20singer%20and%20actress%20Jane%20Birkin%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20coveted%20luxury%20items%20in%20the%20world%20%E2%80%93%20its%20origin%20story%20is%20less%20glamorous%2C%20however.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Birkin%20handbag%20was%20conceived%20by%20Birkin%20herself%2C%20who%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fjane-birkin-dead-at-76-life-in-photos-2023-7%3F_gl%3D1*16070nr*_ga*NTYyMzQ1Njc4LjE2ODU1NjkyNjM.*_ga_E21CV80ZCZ*MTY4OTU4MzA0My4yMzEuMS4xNjg5NTkzOTYzLjQ1LjAuMA..%5C%22%3Efound%20dead%20at%20her%20home%20in%20Paris%20on%20Sunday%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20cause%20of%20her%20death%20is%20not%20yet%20known%2C%20though%20Birkin%20reportedly%20suffered%20from%20health%20issues%20after%20a%20stroke%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20revealed%20the%20story%20behind%20the%20handbag%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vogue.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fjane-birkin-hermes-bag%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVogue%20contributor%20Luke%20Leitch%20in%202012%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201981%2C%20Birkin%20found%20herself%20sitting%20next%20to%20Jean-Louis%20Dumas%20%E2%80%93%20who%20was%20chairman%20of%20French%20luxury%20design%20house%20Herm%C3%A9s%20at%20the%20time%20%E2%80%93%20when%20she%20was%20upgraded%20by%20Air%20France%20on%20a%20flight%20to%20London%2C%20she%20told%20Leitch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20spilling%20the%20contents%20of%20her%20handbag%20on%20the%20plane%20floor%2C%20Dumas%20said%20to%20her%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20should%20have%20one%20with%20pockets%2C%26quot%3B%20to%20which%20she%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20day%20Herm%C3%A8s%20makes%20one%20with%20pockets%20I%20will%20have%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDumas%20reportedly%20responded%3A%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20am%20Herm%C3%A8s%2C%20and%20I%20will%20put%20pockets%20in%20for%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20drew%20the%20design%20of%20a%20handbag%20she%20wanted%20on%20an%20airplane%20sickness%20bag.%20Dumas%20agreed%20to%20make%20it%20for%20her%20on%20the%20condition%20that%20she'd%20let%20him%20use%20her%20surname%20as%20the%20name%20of%20the%20bag.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBirkin%20told%20Leitch%20that%20Herm%C3%A9s%20paid%20her%20an%20annual%20royalty%20of%20%C2%A330%2C000%20in%202011%2C%20which%20currently%20works%20out%20as%20%2439%2C000.%20She%20then%20distributed%20this%20income%20to%20her%20chosen%20charities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYears%20later%2C%20the%20Birkin%20handbag%20has%20taken%20on%20a%20life%20of%20its%20own%20and%20is%20now%20seen%20as%20a%20status%20symbol.%20Customers%20have%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20years-long%20waiting%20lists%20to%20buy%20the%20bag%20from%20one%20of%20its%20stores.%20The%20scarcity%20of%20these%20items%20has%20created%20a%20booming%20resale%20market%2C%20where%20Birkins%20sell%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhermes-birkin-bag-realreal-handbag-expert-so-expensive-2019-6%5C%22%3Ethousands%20of%20dollars%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Df1bb827c2efd1bbe3dc2cf92a4b9ffe8c772dc1b8ed2dea06b6b4e707ff220d4%26postID%3D64b51bafb854d55485189035%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.sothebys.com%252Fen%252Farticles%252Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-the-hermes-birkin%2523%253A~%253Atext%253DBirkin%2525