n%20and%20coming%20of%20online%20media%20platforms%20(OTT)%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20phenomenal%20rise%20of%20regional%20cinema%20in%20India.%20New%20media%20and%20digital%20technologies%20have%20propelled%20regional%20cinema%20to%20conquer%20new%20territories.%20Films%20made%20in%20Marathi%2C%20Punjabi%2C%20Malayalam%2C%20Telugu%2C%20etc.%20have%20been%20popular%20beyond%20their%20language%20markets.%20Could%20this%20also%20happen%20with%20Maithili%20cinema%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20during%20the%20San%20Sebastian%20International%20Film%20Festival%2C%20young%20film%20director%20Parth%20Saurabh%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EPokhar%20Ke%20Dunu%20Paar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(On%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20pond)%20got%20the%20%E2%80%98Special%20Mention%20New%20Directors%20award%E2%80%99.%20Based%20in%20Darbhanga%2C%20it%20has%20not%20been%20released%20yet%20in%20cinema%20halls%20or%20on%20any%20OTT%20platform%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20being%20discussed%20in%20the%20festival%20circuit.%20Next%20month%2C%20it%20will%20be%20screened%20at%20the%20Indian%20Film%20Festival%20of%20Melbourne%20along%20with%20Anurag%20Kashyap%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EKennedy%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20history%20of%20Maithili%20films%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaithili%20film%20history%20is%20more%20than%2050%20years%20old.%20%3Cem%3EKanyadan%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20based%20on%20famous%20Maithili%20writer%20Harimohan%20Jha%E2%80%99s%20novel%20of%20the%20same%20name%20(1933)%2C%20directed%20by%20Phani%20Mazumdar%2C%20which%20was%20released%20in%201971%2C%20is%20credited%20with%20being%20the%20first%20Maithili%20film.%20It%20depicts%20the%20problem%20of%20mismatched%20marriage%20through%20language%20problems%20in%20pre-independent%20India.%20Nabendu%20Ghosh%20wrote%20its%20script%20while%20famous%20Hindi%20writer%20Phanishwar%20Nath%20%E2%80%9CRenu%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20the%20dialogue%20for%20%3Cem%3EKanyadan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17181904%2Fimage-1128.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22847%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17181904%2Fimage-1128.png%20707w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17181904%2Fimage-1128-300x137.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663645%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22387%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20the%20Maithili%20movie%2C%20%3Cem%3EKanyadan%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Photo%3A%20YouTube%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20%3Cem%3EKanyadan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20Maithili-speaking%20filmmaker%2C%20C.%20Parmanand%2C%20was%20trying%20to%20direct%20the%20first%20Maithili%20film%20in%201964%2C%20named%20%3Cem%3ENaihar%20Bhel%20Mor%20Sasur.%20%3C%2Fem%3EIt%20got%20delayed%20and%20was%20finally%20released%20in%201982%20as%20%3Cem%3EMamta%20Gabay%20Geet%20(Mamta%20sings%20the%20song)%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Both%20the%20movies%20are%20still%20remembered%20for%20their%20sonorous%20songs%20and%20lyrics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Cem%3EMamta%20Gabay%20Geet%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eleading%20playback%20singers%20such%20as%20Geeta%20Dutt%2C%20Mahendra%20Kapoor%20and%20Suman%20Kalyanpur%20gave%20their%20voice.%20When%20I%20was%20in%20school%2C%20I%20remember%20seeing%20it%20on%20Doordarshan%20in%20the%20late%2080s.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20prints%20of%20both%20these%20films%20are%20not%20available%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20Recently%2C%20%3Cem%3EKanyadan%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20uploaded%20on%20YouTube%20but%20it%20is%20incomplete%20and%20not%20in%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20five%20decades%20or%20so%2C%20more%20than%2050%20Maithili%20films%20have%20been%20released%20but%20only%20few%20like%20%3Cem%3EJai%20Baba%20Vaidyanath%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ESasta%20Jingi%20Mahag%20Senur%20(Life%20is%20cheap%2C%20marriage%20is%20expensive)%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EKakhan%20Harab%20Dukh%20Mor%20(When%20will%20my%20sorrow%20go%20away)%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EMithila%20Makhaan%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20etc.%20are%20known%20and%20talked%20about.%20Most%20of%20the%20films%20follow%20the%20narrative%20of%20mainstream%20Hindi%20cinema%20and%20a%20few%20have%20worked%20at%20the%20box%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReleased%20in%201999%2C%20%3Cem%3ESasta%20Jingi%20Mahag%20Senur%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20been%20a%20commercial%20hit%20in%20the%20Mithila%20region.%20Famous%20singers%20like%20Udit%20Narayan%20Jha%2C%20Sadhna%20Sargam%20and%20Suresh%20Wadkar%20were%20associated%20with%20this%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMithila%20Makhaan%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Edirected%20by%20Nitin%20Chandra%2C%20is%20the%20only%20film%20to%20have%20won%20a%20National%20Award%20for%20Best%20Film%20in%20the%20Maithili%20language.%20Though%20%3Cem%3EMithila%20Makhaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20got%20the%20National%20Award%2C%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20a%20theatrical%20release%20and%20was%20finally%20released%20on%20his%20OTT%20platform%2C%20Bejod.in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20Chandra%20released%20his%20new%20Maithili%20thriller%20film%20%3Cem%3EJackson%20Halt%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20Bejod.in.%20Likewise%2C%20last%20year%2C%20during%20the%20International%20Film%20Festival%20of%20India%2C%20a%20Maithili%20film%20%3Cem%3ELotus%20Blooms%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20directed%20by%20Pratik%20Sharma%2C%20was%20screened%20in%20the%20Indian%20Panorama%20section%2C%20but%20is%20yet%20to%20release%20in%20cinema%20halls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20these%20decades%2C%20there%20was%20no%20enthusiasm%20among%20the%20producers-distributors%20regarding%20these%20films.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Feros-cinema-mumbai-art-deco-memories%5C%22%3EWhen%20an%20Old%20Cinema%20Shuts%20Down%2C%20a%20Million%20Memories%20Die%20With%20It%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20lack%20of%20exposure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Bhojpuri%20cinema%20has%20a%20market%20and%20industry%2C%20Maithili%20cinema%20has%20failed%20to%20develop%20a%20market%20while%20cinema%20production%20in%20both%20the%20languages%20started%20simultaneously%20in%20the%201960s.%20Maithili%20may%20not%20be%20as%20widespread%20as%20Bhojpuri%2C%20which%20is%20spoken%20in%20several%20states%2C%20but%20it%20still%20has%20approximately%2013%20million%20speakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActually%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20lack%20of%20support%20and%20distribution%20network%20for%20Maithili%20films%20in%20all%20these%20years%2C%20which%20is%20true%20even%20in%20the%20age%20of%20OTT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%2C%20well-known%20film%20director%20Girish%20Kasaravalli%20had%20told%20me%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20idea%20of%20online%20platforms%20came%2C%20we%20thought%20it%20would%20help%20the%20small%20filmmakers%2C%20but%20our%20expectations%20did%20not%20come%20true.%20OTT%20is%20more%20concerned%20about%20returns%2C%20profits%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20Kerala%20recently%20started%20a%20government-owned%20OTT%20platform%20to%20screen%20off-beat%20Malayalam%20films%20that%20have%20received%20critical%20acclaim%20and%20national%20and%20international%20attention.%20I%20thought%20that%20was%20a%20very%20good%20move.%20In%20this%20regard%2C%20Kerala%20has%20taken%20the%20lead%2C%20and%20others%20should%20follow.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%2C%20the%20Bihar%20government%20will%20take%20the%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaithili%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mha.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FEighthSchedule_19052017.pdf%5C%22%3Ewas%20included%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Eighth%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20in%202004.%20The%20Mithila%20region%2C%20which%20encompasses%20parts%20of%20North%20Bihar%20and%20Nepal%2C%20is%20known%20for%20its%20rich%20language%2C%20literature%2C%20and%20culture.%20And%20yet%2C%20it%20is%20Bhojpuri%2C%20the%20language%20spoken%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Bihar%2C%20and%20Jharkhand%2C%20that%20has%20produced%20a%20more%20vibrant%20and%20sustainable%20cinema.%20Any%20discussion%20of%20the%20cinema%20of%20Bihar%20begins%20and%20ends%20with%20Bhojpuri%20films.%20It%E2%80%99s%20true%20that%20Bhojpuri%20films%20have%20a%20vast%20catchment%20area%20which%20makes%20them%20commercially%20viable%2C%20but%20unlike%20Bhojpuri%20films%2C%20contemporary%20Maithili%20cinema%20is%20set%20in%20realism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20critical%20acclaim%20of%20movies%20like%20%3Cem%3EGamak%20Ghar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Village%20home)%20and%20%3Cem%3EDhuin%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Fog)%2C%20directed%20by%20Achal%20Mishra%2C%20people%20have%20begun%20noticing%20Maithili%20cinema%20in%20film%20festival%20circuits.%20Last%20year%2C%20%3Cem%3EDhuin%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20screened%20at%20the%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival%20along%20with%20five%20other%20movies.%20Besides%20Cannes%2C%20they%20were%20shown%20at%20the%20Museum%20of%20Modern%20Art%2C%20New%20York%20and%20other%20international%20festivals%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20Maithili%20films%20deal%20with%20the%20issues%20of%20migration%20and%20unemployment%20and%20the%20aspirations%20of%20small%20town%20youth%20in%20a%20globalising%20India.%20While%20%3Cem%3EGamak%20Ghar%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20auto-biographical%20elements%2C%20%3Cem%3EDhuin%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20protagonist%2C%20Pankaj%2C%20is%20an%20aspiring%20young%20theatre%20actor%20who%20is%20dreaming%20to%20make%20it%20big%20one%20day%20in%20Mumbai.%20His%20family%20is%20going%20through%20economic%20hardship%20and%20his%20father%20after%20retirement%20is%20looking%20for%20a%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPartha%20Saurabh%E2%80%99s%20film%2C%20%3Cem%3EPokhar%20ke%20Dunu%20Paar%20%3C%2Fem%3E(On%20either%20side%20of%20the%20pond)%20is%20also%20set%20in%20Darbhanga%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20lockdown.%20Although%20the%20language%20of%20the%20film%20is%20Hindi%2C%20the%20lilt%20of%20Maithili%20is%20heard%20in%20every%20frame.%20Here%20the%20story%20revolves%20around%20patriarchy%20and%20unemployment.%20The%20film%20does%20not%20provide%20any%20answers%20but%20rather%20asks%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20and%20offers%20a%20sharp%20comment%20on%20the%20socio-cultural%20conditions%20of%20our%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20all%20the%20three%20films%20mentioned%20above%2C%20we%20notice%20a%20certain%20minimalism%20and%20visual%20quality%20which%20is%20unheard%20of%20in%20the%20history%20of%20both%20Bhojpuri%20and%20commercial%20Maithili%20cinema.%20%3Cem%3EDhuin%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20poster%20resembles%20that%20of%20well-known%20auteur%20Abbas%20Kiarostami%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EClose%20up%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1990)%20film%20poster.%20During%20a%20conversation%2C%20Mishra%20told%20me%20that%20%E2%80%98he%20is%20influenced%20by%20the%20Iranian%20film%20director%E2%80%99.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20coincidence%20that%20in%20the%20movie%20we%20notice%20a%20scene%20where%20the%20characters%20are%20discussing%20Kiarostami%20in%20Darbhanga.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20era%20of%20blockbusters%20and%20nationalistic%20Bollywood%20films%2C%20these%20movies%20are%20raising%20issues%20which%20concern%20day-to-day%20life%20of%20ordinary%20citizens%2C%20blurring%20the%20linguistic%20and%20aesthetic%20divide.%20But%20they%20need%20to%20get%20exposure%20which%2C%20given%20the%20recognition%20in%20film%20festivals%2C%20will%2C%20it%20is%20hoped%2C%20come%20sooner%20than%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20writer%20is%20a%20journalist%20and%20a%20researcher.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689600630000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17182900%2Fimage-1129.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Famid-a-bollywood-wave-maithili-films-offer-new-perspective-on-societal-issues-but-lack-exposure%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22B