med%20the%20opening%20set%20with%20a%20smash.%20But%20Alcaraz%20finally%20freed%20himself%20of%20his%20shackles%20and%20broke%20for%202-1%20in%20the%20second%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDjokovic%20hit%20straight%20back%20in%20the%20third%20game%20before%20saving%20a%20break%20point%20in%20the%20fourth%2C%20coming%20out%20on%20top%20of%20a%2029-shot%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETime%20violation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Serb%20was%20hit%20with%20a%20time%20violation%20in%20the%20tie-break%20before%20seeing%20a%20set%20point%20saved.%20Alcaraz%20needed%20no%20second%20invitation%20when%20he%20carved%20out%20and%20converted%20a%20set%20point%20to%20level%20the%20contest%20with%20a%20backhand%20winner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20marathon%20set%20had%20taken%2085%20minutes%20as%20Djokovic's%20run%20of%2015%20tie-breaks%20won%20in%20a%20row%20at%20the%20majors%20ended.%20Alcaraz%20broke%20in%20the%20opening%20game%20of%20the%20third%20set%20and%20again%20after%20an%20exhausting%2026-minute%20fifth%20game%2C%20which%20went%20to%2013%20deuces%20and%20saw%20Djokovic%20save%20six%20break%20points%20before%20he%20cracked%20on%20the%20seventh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlcaraz%20backed%20it%20up%20with%20a%20rapid-fire%20service%20game%20which%20took%20just%20two%20minutes%20in%20comparison%20and%20broke%20again%20against%20the%20dispirited%20defending%20champion%20to%20move%20two%20sets%20to%20one%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDjokovic%20broke%20twice%20in%20the%20fourth%20set%2C%20levelling%20the%20match%20courtesy%20of%20Alcaraz's%20seventh%20double%20fault%20of%20the%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Djokovic%20wasted%20a%20golden%20chance%20to%20break%20for%202-0%20in%20the%20decider%20with%20a%20wild%20smash%20and%20Alcaraz%20made%20him%20pay%2C%20breaking%20for%202-1.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERacquet%20outburst%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20frustrated%20Djokovic%20collected%20another%20code%20violation%20for%20destroying%20his%20racquet%20against%20the%20net%20post%20before%20he%20slipped%203-1%20down.%20Alcaraz%20was%20not%20to%20be%20denied%20and%20he%20claimed%20a%20famous%20victory%20when%20Djokovic%20buried%20a%20forehand%20in%20the%20net.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20not%20much%20to%20talk%20about%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Djokovic%20said%20later.%20%26quot%3BSecond%20one%20was%20frustration.%20I%20had%20break%20points%20in%20the%20second%20game.%20Yeah%2C%20just%20tough%2C%20tough%20couple%20of%20points.%20He%20played%20amazing%20to%20break%20my%20serve%2C%20which%20was%20enough%20to%20win%20the%20fifth.%20The%20first%20one%20was%20the%20time%20violation%2C%20so%20yeah.%20Not%20a%20great%20moment%20again%2C%20but%20you%20just%20kind%20of%20have%20to%20accept%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2023-time%20Grand%20Slam%20winner%20was%20further%20prodded%20on%20the%20subject.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20frustration%20in%20the%20moment.%20I%20answered%20to%20your%20colleague%20two%20minutes%20ago%20about%20that.%20There's%20not%20much%20to%20say%20about%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20AFP%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689600360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fs0fil0r_djokovic_625x300_17_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwimbledon-2023%2Ffrustration-what-novak-djokovic-said-on-racquet-outburst-during-wimbledon-final-vs-carlos-alcaraz-4215698%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Australian%20Open%20and%20French%20Open%20champion%20Novak%20Djokovic%20had%20been%20bidding%20to%20equal%20Federer's%20record%20of%20eight%20Wimbledon%20titles%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwimbledon-2023%2Ffrustration-what-novak-djokovic-said-on-racquet-outburst-during-wimbledon-final-vs-carlos-alcaraz-4215698%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwimbledon-2023%2Ffrustration-what-novak-djokovic-said-on-racquet-outburst-during-wimbledon-final-vs-carlos-alcaraz-4215698%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwimbledon-2023%2Ffrustration-what-novak-djokovic-said-on-racquet-outburst-during-wimbledon-final-vs-carlos-alcaraz-4215698%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Analysis%3A%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20The%20Key%20Difference%20Between%20Patna%20And%20Bengaluru%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20opposition%20parties%20get%20down%20to%20their%20second%20unity%20show%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20a%20big%20difference%20from%20Round%20One%20in%20Patna%20is%20the%20presence%20of%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20at%20a%20meeting%20held%20in%20a%20state%20where%20the%20Congress%20is%20firmly%20in%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESonia%20Gandhi's%20presence%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Boutcome%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20first%20meeting%2C%20say%20Congress%20leaders%2C%20but%20they%20are%20hoping%20that%20her%20experience%20as%20a%20coalition%20builder%20before%20the%202004%20polls%20and%20her%20personal%20relationships%20across%20the%20political%20spectrum%20will%20add%20heft%20to%20the%20Congress's%20voice%20at%20the%20negotiating%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESonia%20Gandhi's%20presence%20is%20of%20special%20significance%20in%20Bengaluru.%20The%20Congress's%20chairman%20of%20media%20and%20publicity%2C%20Pawan%20Khera%2C%20emphasizes%2C%20%26quot%3BShe%20is%20a%20senior%20leader%20who%20was%20present%20in%20all%20parliamentary%20meetings%20and%20her%20presence%20will%20give%20strength%20to%20the%20opposition%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20leaders%20of%20most%20alliance%20partners%20had%20once%20rallied%20around%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20chemistry%20may%20help%20move%20things%20forward.%20The%20optics%20also%20sent%20a%20clear%20message%20-%20the%20Congress%20is%20the%20glue%2C%20the%20central%20pole%20around%20which%20the%20opposition%20must%20unite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Patna%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20was%20the%20focus%20and%20the%20question%20was%2C%20who%20is%20bringing%20everyone%20together%3F%20Here%20it%20is%20the%20Congress%20that%20is%20the%20host%20and%20it%20is%20a%20subtle%20reiteration%20of%20the%20party's%20position%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20senior%20leader%20who%20requested%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20taking%20a%20stand%20on%20the%20Centre's%20ordinance%20on%20the%20control%20of%20administrative%20services%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20seemingly%20projecting%20a%20more%20conciliatory%20image.%20The%20move%20signals%20its%20willingness%20to%20make%20concessions%20and%20ensure%20that%2C%20despite%20the%20historic%20animosity%2C%20there%20is%20an%20effort%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP).%20This%20may%20be%20an%20indication%2C%20beyond%20AAP%2C%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20willing%20to%20give%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20build%20a%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20ensure%20that%20the%20Congress-AAP%20friction%20does%20not%20end%20up%20ruining%20the%20effort%20and%20the%20optics%20is%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20substance%2C%20though%20the%20location%20of%20the%20meeting%20is%20in%20southern%20India%2C%20the%20substantive%20dialogue%20will%20revolve%20around%20electoral%20strategy%20in%20the%20BJP's%20bastion%2C%20the%20northern%20states.%20This%20is%20because%20alliances%20in%20the%20southern%20states%2C%20barring%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%2C%20seem%20set.%20The%20DMK%20is%20in%20charge%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20the%20Congress%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20a%20Left%20versus%20Congress%20battle%20in%20Kerala%20-%20par%20for%20the%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelangana%20Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20and%20Andhra%20Chief%20Minister%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20are%20unlikely%20allies%20and%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20seems%20to%20be%20heading%20to%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA).%20This%20makes%20coalitions%20in%20South%20India%20relatively%20straightforward%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20in%20the%20northern%20states%20that%20creating%20this%20rainbow%20coalition%20and%20getting%20it%20right%20is%20essential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20leader%20pointed%20out%20that%20Sonia%20Gandhi's%20presence%20and%20experience%20could%20help%2C%20especially%20with%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20Samajwadi%20Party.%20The%20two%20parties%20have%20had%20uncomfortable%20equations%20in%20the%20past%2C%20and%20firming%20up%20the%20tenets%20of%20the%20alliance%20in%20states%20like%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Bihar%20will%20be%20the%20launch%20pad%20for%20opposition%20unity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20sense%20that%20leaders%20like%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20or%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20who%20are%20of%20similar%20vintage%20as%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20would%20respond%20much%20better%20to%20Sonia%20Gandhi.%20Even%20with%20older%20allies%20like%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20Lalu%20Yadav%2C%20the%20Sonia%20factor%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20better%20play.%20It%20is%20something%20that%20is%20beyond%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge's%20experience%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20enthusiasm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crisis%20in%20Maharashtra%20is%20a%20focal%20point%2C%20but%20on%20the%20whole%2C%20unlike%20Patna%2C%20there%20is%20an%20expectation%20of%20some%20concrete%20forward%20movement%20and%20greater%20cohesion%20after%20this%20meeting.%20While%20it%20is%20still%20nascent%2C%20two%20points%20seem%20to%20be%20emerging.%20First%2C%20the%20reiteration%20of%20Congress%20as%20the%20central%20force%20bringing%20the%20%26quot%3BMahagathbandhan%26quot%3B%20together%2C%20and%20second%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20may%20still%20hold%20sway%20and%20be%20part%20of%20the%20opposition's%20battle%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20started%20prepping%20its%20own%20show%20of%20strength%20by%20reengaging%20with%20some%20former%20allies%20and%20reaching%20out%20to%20others%2C%20the%20opposition%20will%20need%20som