combat%20conditions%20in%20Ukraine.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Minnie%20Chan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrill-hints-at-chinese-military-lessons-from-russia-ukraine-war-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Double-Engine%20Govt%20in%20Uttarakhand%20Flouted%20Rules%20To%20Allow%20River%20Mining%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17172929%2FSand-mining-underway-in-a-river.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20An%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reporters-collective.in%2Ftrc%2Fas-cm-lobbied-centre-went-against-rules-courts-to-allow-river-mining-in-uttarakhand%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Einvestigation%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Reporters%E2%80%99%20Collective%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(TRC)%3Cspan%3E%20has%20revealed%20that%20the%20Uttarakhand%20government%20enjoys%20impunity%20in%20flouting%20environmental%20norms%20as%20it%20pushes%20for%20increased%20mining%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Gaula%20river.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Gaula%20is%20already%20dying%20due%20to%20excessive%20mining%20and%20deforestation%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETRC%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20report%20says%2C%20but%20this%20has%20not%20deterred%20the%20Union%20government%20from%20extending%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20permission%20to%20mine%20from%20the%20river.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Union%20environment%20ministry%20is%20also%20undeterred%20by%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20unwillingness%20to%20comply%20with%20rules%20meant%20to%20protect%20the%20environment.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETRC%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reports%20that%20it%20has%20also%20relaxed%20existing%20environmental%20regulations%2C%20allowing%20the%20state%20government%20to%20further%20degrade%20the%20Gaula.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFlowing%20through%20eastern%20Uttarakhand%2C%20the%20Gaula%20originates%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Nainital%20district%20and%20eventually%20joins%20the%20Ramganga%20river%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20joins%20the%20Ganges%20further%20downstream.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20passes%20through%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Haldwani%20city%20as%20it%20enters%20the%20plains%20and%20is%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsandrp.in%2F2021%2F10%2F02%2Fa-day-along-the-goula-river-in-haldwani%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eimportant%20source%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20water%20for%20the%20city.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20its%20course%2C%20the%20Gaula%20collects%20stones%20and%20minerals%20from%20upstream%20and%20deposits%20them%20in%20the%20plains.%20These%20also%20regulate%20the%20Gaula%E2%80%99s%20flow%2C%20and%20unfettered%20mining%20risks%20allowing%20the%20river%20to%20take%20unprecedented%20paths%20downstream%20during%20the%20monsoon%20and%20damage%20farmland%20as%20well%20as%20bridges%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETRC%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFlooding%20from%20rivers%20is%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fnorth-india-rains-landslide-floods-toll%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emajor%20cause%20of%20destruction%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20during%20the%20monsoon%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fbadrinath-redevelopment-must-respect-its-heritage%5C%22%3ERedevelopment%20Projects%20at%20Badrinath%20Must%20Respect%20its%20Unique%20Natural%20and%20Spiritual%20Heritage%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20statutory%20body%20in%20the%20Uttarakhand%20government%2C%20known%20as%20the%20Uttarakhand%20Forest%20Development%20Corporation%20(UFDC)%2C%20was%20granted%20permission%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20mine%20the%20Gaula%20for%2010%20years%20starting%20in%20January%202013%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETRC%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20government%20attempted%20to%20renew%20this%20permission%20starting%20in%20April%202022%2C%20and%20obtained%20a%20temporary%20extension%20from%20the%20Union%20environment%20ministry%20in%20January%20this%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETRC%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reports%20that%20the%20ministry%20granted%20this%20temporary%20extension%20without%20knowing%20the%20full%20extent%20of%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20compliance%20with%20forest%20conservation%20rules%20%E2%80%93%20as%20the%20latter%20submitted%20only%20an%20incomplete%20compliance%20report%20%E2%80%93%20even%20though%20it%20should%20take%20this%20information%20into%20consideration%20as%20per%20regulations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20even%20with%20the%20available%20information%2C%20the%20ministry%20noted%20that%20Uttarakhand%20violated%20forestry%20conditions%20by%20allowing%20construction%20works%20in%20areas%20marked%20for%20compensatory%20afforestation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20month%20later%2C%20the%20Uttarakhand%20government%20obtained%20a%20permanent%20extension%20of%20its%20permission%20to%20mine%20the%20Gaula%20from%20the%20Union%20ministry%2C%20although%20by%20only%20half%20its%20requested%20period%20of%2010%20years%2C%20owing%20to%20its%20poor%20compliance%20with%20conditions%20imposed%20on%20it%20from%20a%20previous%20approval%2C%20according%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3ETRC%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Union%20ministry%20also%20granted%20permission%20to%20Uttarakhand%20to%20mine%20the%20Gaula%20through%20June%20this%20year%2C%20relaxing%20its%20own%20guidelines%20prohibiting%20the%20mining%20of%20rivers%20during%20the%20monsoon%20in%20order%20to%20allow%20them%20to%20recover%20from%20the%20effects%20of%20mining.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20use%20of%20forest%20conservation%20and%20environment%20protection%20laws%20and%20policy%20if%20those%20going%20against%20them%20are%20allowed%20to%20exploit%20resources%20and%20are%20given%20relaxations%20to%20do%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20environmental%20lawyer%20Rahul%20Choudhary%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETRC%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20violating%20compliance%20conditions%20under%20forest%20conservation%20laws%20can%20amount%20to%20violating%20the%20law%20itself.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20the%20purpose%20of%20%5Bthe%5D%20law%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20openly%20flouted%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fjoshimath-himalayas-explainer-warnings-reports-construction-ntpc%5C%22%3EUncontrolled%20Construction%2C%20Ignored%20Warnings%3A%20How%20Joshimath%20Sank%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPushkar%20Singh%20Dhami%2C%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20chief%20minister%2C%20announced%20the%20renewal%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20mining%20permission%20(which%20was%20also%20granted%20in%20relation%20to%20three%20other%20rivers)%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post%2C%20where%20he%20thanked%20the%20Union%20environment%20minister%20and%20attributed%20this%20success%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdouble-engine%20government%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20used%20the%20term%20double-engine%20government%20to%20refer%20to%20the%20Union%20and%20Uttarakhand%20governments%20being%20ruled%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(