y.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandra%20left%20the%20scene%20of%20the%20crash%20and%20returned%20home%20without%20reporting%20what%20occurred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDaniel%20Hawkins%2C%20Jacob%20Ivascu%2C%20and%20Drake%20Ruiz%2C%20all%2016%2C%20were%20killed.%20The%2018-year-old%20driver%20of%20the%20Prius%20as%20well%20as%20two%20other%20boys%20ages%2013%20and%2014%2C%20were%20injured%20but%20survived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20said%20that%20the%20boys%20were%20having%20a%20sleepover%20and%20ultimately%20dared%20one%20of%20the%20friends%20to%20do%20a%20%26quot%3Bdoorbell%20ditch%2C%26quot%3B%20so%20they%20drove%20to%20a%20nearby%20house%2C%20according%20to%20an%20investigation%20by%20the%20California%20Highway%20Patrol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20there%2C%20one%20of%20the%20boys%20rang%20the%20doorbell%20of%20a%20home%20on%20Modjeska%20Summit%20Road%20and%20ran%20back%20to%20their%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandra%2C%20who%20lived%20at%20the%20home%2C%20chased%20after%20the%20boys'%20vehicle%20in%20his%20own%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Chandra%20pursued%20the%20victims%2C%20he%20re-ended%20the%20Prius%20and%20sideswiped%20their%20vehicle%20until%20they%20were%20forced%20to%20stop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boys%20made%20a%20U-turn%20to%20escape%2C%20however%2C%20Chandra%20continued%20his%20pursuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20as%20both%20vehicles%20approached%20Squaw%20Mountain%20Road%2C%20Chandra%20increased%20his%20speed%20to%2099%20mph%2C%20then%20intentionally%20rammed%20his%20car%20into%20the%20back%20of%20the%20Prius%2C%20causing%20it%20to%20veer%20off%20the%20road%20and%20into%20a%20tree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20case%2C%20Chandra%20also%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20misdemeanour%20charges%20of%20spousal%20battery%20and%20child%20endangerment%20and%20received%20credit%20for%20time%20already%20served.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandra%20has%20been%20in%20custody%20at%20the%20Robert%20Presley%20Detention%20Centre%20in%20Riverside%20since%20h