%2Fnews%2Freliance-to-acquire-alia-bhatt-promoted-kidswear-brand-ed-a-mamma-123071700691_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bond%20ETFs%20surpass%20%242%20trillion%20milestone%20as%20asset%20growth%20'explodes'%20-%20and%20BlackRock%20believes%20this%20is%20just%20the%20beginning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221885%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20word%20%26quot%3Bbonds%26quot%3B%20on%20wooden%20cubes%20with%20office%20desktop.%20Business%20finance%20stock%20exchange%20concept.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b5211964dab3001999e8cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWealthfront%20launches%20new%20automated%20bond%20portfolio%20that%20invests%20in%20bond%20ETFs%3Cp%3Ecagkansayin%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBond%20ETFs%20just%20hit%20a%20new%20milestone%20-%20with%20assets%20under%20management%20surpassing%20%242%20trillion%20to%20reach%20a%20record.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%C2%A0BlackRock%2C%20the%20world's%20largest%20asset%20manager%2C%20sees%20the%20sector%20tripling%20in%20size%20to%20%246%20trillion%20by%202030.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBond%20ETFs%20are%20becoming%20popular%20amid%20demand%20for%20the%20relative%20safety%20of%20debt%2C%20and%20as%20inflation%20rapidly%20cools.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20market%20for%20exchange-traded%20funds%20that%20invest%20in%20bonds%20is%20booming%20%E2%80%93%20the%20total%20value%20of%20such%20plans%20have%20just%20surged%20past%20%242%20trillion%20to%20a%20new%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20the%20bond%20ETF%20industry%2C%20which%20came%20into%20existence%20in%202002%2C%20as%20many%20as%2017%20years%20to%20reach%20its%20first%20%241%20trillion%2C%20but%20it%20saw%20the%20amount%20double%20in%20just%204%20years%2C%20according%20to%20VettaFi%2C%20a%20firm%20that%20specializes%20in%20asset-management%20data%20and%20analytics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlackRock%2C%20the%20world's%20largest%20money%20manager%2C%20sees%20the%20market%20for%20bond%20ETFs%20tripling%20to%20%246%20trillion%20by%202030%2C%20according%20to%20an%20investor%20presentation%20it%20released%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESurging%20inflows%20into%20debt-focused%20funds%20likely%20reflects%20increasing%20investor%20demand%20for%20the%20safety%20and%20stability%20of%20bonds%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20more%20volatile%20nature%20of%20riskier%20assets%20such%20as%20stocks.%20Flows%20into%20bond%20ETFs%20first%20started%20accelerating%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20global%20financial%20crisis%20of%202008%2C%20which%20rocked%20risk%20assets%20worldwide%2C%20according%20to%20VettaFi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20bond%20ETFs%20really%20took%20off%20during%20the%20more%20recent%20spells%20of%20market%20volatility%20%E2%80%93%20in%20early%202020%2C%20amid%20the%20outbreak%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20and%20then%20in%202022%2C%20when%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20raised%20interest%20rates%20at%20a%20pace%20unseen%20in%20decades%20to%20quell%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20just%20passed%20this%20tremendous%20milestone%2C%26quot%3B%20Todd%20Rosenbluth%2C%20head%20of%20research%20at%20VettaFi%2C%20said%20in%20a%20recent%20tweet%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20%242%20trillion%C2%A0%20mark.%20Still%2C%20ETFs%20currently%20make%20up%20only%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20vast%20%24133%20trillion%20bond%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20conventional%20bond%20market%20is%20driven%20by%20over-the-counter%20trades%20between%20institutions%2C%20ETFs%2C%20as%20indicated%20by%20their%20name%2C%20are%20traded%20on%20an%20exchange.%20A%20single%20ETF%20can%20given%20investors%20exposure%20to%20large%20numbers%20of%20bonds%2C%C2%A0%20thereby%20providing%20increased%20portfolio%20diversification%20and%20liquidity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20current%20economic%20climate%2C%20as%20US%20inflation%20cools%20and%20interest%20rates%20approach%20a%20peak%2C%20demand%20for%20fixed-income%20products%20is%20on%20the%20rise.%20The%20prospect%20of%20lower%20inflation%20and%20rates%20is%20positive%20for%20debt%20securities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbond-etfs-hit-record-2-trillion-growth-explodes-blackrock-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689596314000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b5211964dab3001999e8cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Fbond-etfs-hit-record-2-trillion-growth-explodes-blackrock-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20market%20for%20exchange-traded%20funds%20that%20invest%20in%20bonds%20is%20booming%20%E2%80%93%20the%20total%20value%20of%20such%20plans%20have%20just%20surged%20past%20%242%20trillion%20to%20a%20new%20record.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jwilkins%40insider.com%20(Joseph%20Wilkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Seat-Sharing%20Big%20Test%20As%20Opposition%20Eyes%20Common%20Minimum%20Programme%20In%20Meet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETop%20leaders%20of%2026%20opposition%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20are%20expected%20to%20attend%20the%20two-day%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fseat-sharing-plan-for-2024-polls-monsoon-session-agenda-at-opposition-meet-4213591%5C%22%3Ebrainstorming%20session%20in%20Bengaluru%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20today.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20important%20tasks%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20these%20parties%20is%20to%20set%20the%20ball%20rolling%20on%20a%20possible%20Common%20Minimum%20Programme%20that%20can%20help%20them%20function%20smoothly%2C%20address%20their%20political%20compulsions%20and%20the%20few%20ideological%20contradictions%20that%20exist%20among%20them.%20Congress%20leaders%20have%20said%20that%20a%20sub-committee%20will%20also%20be%20formed%20for%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20a%20Common%20Minimum%20Programme%20or%20national%20agenda%20for%20governance%20is%20not%20uncommon%20in%20India%20which%20has%20seen%20many%20political%20alliances%20at%20the%20centre.%20A%20CMP%20is%20usually%20a%20set%20of%20policies%20and%20programmes%20that%20all%20partners%20of%20an%20alliance%20agree%20to%20abide%20by%20for%20the%20smooth%20functioning%20of%20the%20alliance%2C%20also%20outlining%20what%20the%20front%20plans%20to%20do%2C%20basically%20setting%20a%20broad%20agenda%20that%20is%20agreeable%20to%20all%20parties%20involved.%20The%20major%20coalitions%20--%20the%20United%20Front%20in%201996%2C%20BJP-led%20NDA%20from%201998%20to%202004%20and%20Congress-led%20UPA%20from%202004%20to%202014%20-%20were%20all%20post-poll%20arrangements%20with%20parties%20and%20all%20of%20them%20had%20a%20documented%20common%20agenda%20of%20sorts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201994%2C%20when%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies%20won%20only%20217%20seats%2C%20it%20had%20to%20be%20supported%20by%20the%20Left%20Front%20which%20had%20won%2063%20seats%20in%20that%20election.%20A%20CMP%20was%20then%20created%20to%20have%20one%20programme%20that%20all%20the%20allies%20would%20agree%20to%20and%20which%20the%20government%20can%20then%20implement.%20A%20committee%20under%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20was%20asked%20to%20do%20this.%20The%20committee%20also%20had%20other%20members%2C%20such%20as%20Pranab%20Mukherjee%20and%20Jairam%20Ramesh.%20In%201996%2C%20it%20was%20CPM's%20Sitaram%20Yechury%20along%20with%20P%20Chidambaram%20and%20S%20Jaipal%20Reddy%20who%20had%20drafted%20the%20United%20Front%20government's%20CMP%2C%20which%20was%20also%20integrated%20in%20the%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20Deve%20Gowda%20government's%20budget%20for%201996-1997.%20The%20Atal%20Bihar%20Vajpayee%20government%20that%20consisted%20of%20over%2020%20parties%20too%20had%20an%20%26quot%3BAgenda%20for%20Development%2C%20Good%20Governance%20and%20Peace%26quot%3B.%20This%20NDA%20alliance%20was%20perhaps%20the%20largest%20coalition%20that%20brought%20together%20many%20regional%20parties%20who%20agreed%20to%20be%20part%20of%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20provided%20the%20party's%20core%20agenda%20like%20Ram%20Temple%2C%20Article%20370%20and%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20are%20kept%20on%20the%20back-burner.%20Most%20of%20the%20regional%20parties%20except%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20Bahujan%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20RJD%2C%20and%20the%20Left%20were%20part%20of%20the%20NDA%20at%20one%20point%20of%20time%20or%20another%20from%201998%20to%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20parties%20had%20different%20views%20on%20foreign%20policy%2C%20national%20security%2C%20economic%20policies%20and%20even%20social%20welfare.%20Apart%20from%20Hindutva%20issues%2C%20divestment%20or%20running%20of%20PSUs%2C%20foreign%20policy%20matters%20have%20been%20common%20points%20of%20disagreement%20between%20parties%20when%20it%20came%20to%20framing%20a%20common%20agenda.%20Most%20of%20the%20CMPs%20till%20now%20have%20been%20more%20of%20a%20document%20showing%20consensus%20to%20work%20together%2C%20high%20on%20intent%20but%20short%20on%20strategy%2C%20often%20falling%20apart%20over%20promises%20not%20kept%2C%20particularly%20as%20elections%20closed%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20that%2026%20parties%20are%20meeting%20in%20Bengaluru%20for%20a%20two-day%20conclave%2C%20there%20will%20be%20subcommittees%20put%20in%20place%20to%20devise%20a%20CMP%20and%20also%20decide%20on%20joint%20rallies.%20However%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20attempts%20being%20made%20to%20foster%20opposition%20unity%20now%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%202024%2C%20it%20is%20the%20practical%20working%20of%20the%20alliance%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20will%20count%2C%20more%20than%20the%20ideological%20considerations%20that%20remain%20far%20and%20few%20between.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20how%20will%20the%20seat-sharing%20work%20out%20between%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20the%20Congress%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20The%20Congress%20is%20fighting%20the%20TMC%20tooth%20and%20nail%20and%20Trinamool%20has%20managed%20to%20wipe%20out%20the%20Congress%20electorally%20from%20even%20its%20strongholds%20in%20the%20state.%20There%20is%20also%20this%20challenge%20of%20what%20the%20Congress%20will%20do%20in%20Punjab%20and%20Delhi.%20There%20are%20about%2022%20seats%20where%20the%20Congress%20faces%20the%20AAP%20in%20these%20places.%20Will%20the%20Congress%20leave%20them%20for%20AAP%3F%20And%20what%20happens%20in%20Maharashtra%20is%20also%20another%20big%20question%2C%20specifically%20because%20both%20the%20NCP%20and%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20have%20quit.%20But%2C%20considering%20it%20is%20the%20first%20time%20in%20many%20years%20that%2026%20non-BJP%20parties%20are%20engaging%20with%20one%20another%20in%20a%20pre-poll%20set%20up%20and%20also%20with%20the%20Congress%20playing%20a%20role%2C%20this%20is%20an%20attempt%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20closely%20watch%20and%20push%20with%20all%20its%20might%20to%20counter.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689596280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Flt8orkok_bengaluru-opposition-meet-ani_625x300_17_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fopposition-bengaluru-meet-common-minimum-programme-2024-blueprint-key-agenda-in-opposition-meet-the-challenges-ahead-4215091%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Top%20leaders%20of%2026%20opposition%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20are%20expected%20to%20attend%20the%20two-day%20brainstorming%20session%20in%20Bengaluru%20from%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fopposition-bengaluru-meet-common-minimum-programme-2024-blueprint-key-agenda-in-opposition-meet-the-challenges-ah