22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fselectors-and-board-should-be-asking-questions-sunil-gavaskar-unhappy-over-indias-wtc-final-strategy-4215339%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fselectors-and-board-should-be-asking-questions-sunil-gavaskar-unhappy-over-indias-wtc-final-strategy-4215339%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Karnataka%20govt%20offers%20additional%20100%20acres%20land%20to%20Foxconn%20for%20proposed%20Rs%208%2C800%20crore%20plant%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689595820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101830411%2Cimgsize-123768.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fkarnataka-govt-offers-additional-100-acres-to-foxconn-for-proposed-rs-8800-crore-plant%2Farticleshow%2F101829577.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22SANDEEP%20MOUDGAL%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fkarnataka-govt-offers-additional-100-acres-to-foxconn-for-proposed-rs-8800-crore-plant%2Farticleshow%2F101829577.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blog%3A%20A%20Student's%20Guide%20To%20Hustle%20Culture%20And%20Its%20Fallout%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIs%20it%20ever%20enough%3F%20When%20do%20we%20know%20we've%20made%20it%3F%20The%20number%20of%20cars%20we%20own%3F%20Or%20launching%20a%20start-up%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20never%20really%20seems%20enough.%20This%20drives%20students%2C%20entrepreneurs%2C%20and%20employees%20to%20work%20long%20hours%2C%20moonlight%2C%20and%20skew%20their%20work-life%20balance%2C%20just%20to%20make%20the%20extra%20buck.%20But%20the%20glamorisation%20of%20such%20a%20lifestyle%20neglects%20self-care%2C%20mental%20wellness%20and%20physical%20health.%20Too%20much%20of%20anything%20is%20never%20good.%20Too%20much%20work%20and%20limited%20play%20could%20lead%20to%20the%20worst%20outcome%20-%20burnout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20sets%20us%20up%20for%20a%20deep%20dive%20into%20Hustle%20Culture%20-%20a%20predominantly%20Western%20approach%20to%20work%20that%20idealises%20extreme%20hard%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangalore's%20demographic%20is%20a%20cosmopolitan%20mix%20of%20people%2C%20nationally%20and%20internationally%2C%20seeking%20more%20sustainable%20job%20opportunities%20and%20a%20better%20life.%20Over%20half%20the%20current%20population%20is%20migrants%20and%20influenced%20by%20multiple%20cultures%2C%20and%20the%20one%20that%20sticks%20out%20is%20the%20Hustle%20Culture.%20Its%20definition%20of%20success%20is%20problematic%20and%20must%20come%20undone%20because%20it%20sets%20unrealistic%20and%20materialistic%20expectations%20for%20happiness%2C%20recognition%20and%20validation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengaluru%20is%20witnessing%20waves%20of%20entrepreneurs%2C%20freelancers%20and%20remote%20part-timers%20of%20all%20ages%20in%20the%20name%20of%20%26quot%3Bhustling%26quot%3B%20for%20self-reliance.%20The%20concept%20of%20%26quot%3Bwork%26quot%3B%20has%20evolved%20from%20a%20directed%20and%20administered%20framework%20to%20self-motivation%2C%20guilt%20and%20toxic%20positivity%20that%20ignores%20the%20importance%20of%20expressing%20one's%20boundaries%20honestly%20without%20crippling%20anxiety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20any%20of%20this%20resonates%20with%20you%2C%20and%20you%20want%20to%20protect%20your%20mental%20and%20physical%20health%2C%20open%20your%20eyes%20to%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20hustler%20lifestyle%20and%20understand%20that%20you%20may%20not%20end%20up%20happy%20because%20it%20is%20a%20model%20based%20on%20the%20idealism%20of%20influencers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengaluru's%20cultural%20diversity%20reflects%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20social%20media%20impacts%20the%20population.%20The%20habit%20of%20working%20relentlessly%20hard%20was%2C%20in%20the%20past%2C%20typical%20of%20marginalised%20communities%20trying%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20However%2C%20the%20youth%20today%2C%20with%20increased%20exposure%20to%20social%20media%2C%20are%20driven%20to%20make%20unsettling%20changes%20to%20their%20worldview%2C%20altering%20their%20perception%20of%20what%20is%20essential%2C%20and%20placing%20value%20on%20a%20lifestyle%20that%20glorifies%20the%20West%20for%20its%20abundance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20desire%20for%20success%20is%20not%20the%20problem%2C%20but%20how%20it%20infringes%20upon%20their%20personal%20life%20and%20tips%20the%20balance%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20pattern%20of%20increasing%20mental%20and%20physical%20health%20issues.%20With%20all%20the%20information%20and%20progressive%20thought%20on%20mental%20health%2C%20the%20stigma%20remains%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20work%20because%20working%20harder%20is%20associated%20with%20fewer%20problems%20in%20life%20and%20negative%20feelings%20are%20received%20as%20pessimistic%20and%20unhealthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20good%20leader%20needs%20a%20steadying%20force%3B%20unfortunately%2C%20this%20generation%20uses%20social%20media%20which%20is%20regulated%20by%20inconsistent%20algorithms%2C%20as%20their%20compass.%20The%20hustle%20culture%20also%20quantifies%20success%20in%20monetary%20terms%3B%20money%20signifies%20self-reliance%2C%20a%20marker%20of%20achievement.%20However%2C%20people%20must%20acknowledge%20that%20success%20is%20also%20about%20knowing%20how%20to%20approach%20others%20when%20help%20is%20needed.%20Motivational%20speakers%20and%20self-help%20guides%20give%20much%20importance%20to%20doing%20everything%20yourself%2C%20repeating%20that%20you%20are%20your%20greatest%20asset%20and%20that%20you%20alone%20can%20get%20you%20to%20the%20level%20you%20want%20to%20achieve.%20However%2C%20this%20mental%20toughness%20is%20fragile%20because%20social%20media%20dynamics%20adapt%20to%20every%20trend%2C%20leaving%20people%20with%20wavering%20goals%20and%20a%20rocky%20road%20map%20to%20achieve%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHustlers%20are%20bound%20to%20burn%20out%20without%20balance%20and%20consistency%2C%20and%20erratic%20work%20cultures%20make%20it%20difficult%20to%20find%20a%20system%20in%20which%20their%20job%20and%20personal%20life%20can%20function%20symbiotically.%20The%20key%20to%20living%20on%20both%20ends%20of%20the%20spectrum%20is%20to%20remember%20to%20bounce%20between%20deep%20work%20and%20deep%20rest.%20Avoid%20idolising%20expectations%20that%20you%20struggle%20to%20meet%20during%20the%20week%2C%20which%20spill%20over%20to%20the%20weekend%2C%20taking%20away%20the%20time%20needed%20to%20rejuvenate%20the%20mind%20and%20body%20for%20the%20next%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrioritise%20your%20personal%2C%20emotional%20and%20physical%20needs%20as%20much%20as%20your%20career%2C%20and%20detach%20from%20work%20when%20you're%20away.%20If%20needed%2C%20engage%20in%20mental%20prioritisation%20by%20allocating%20a%20dedicated%20hour%20or%20two%20at%20the%20weekend%20to%20complete%20the%20unavoidable%2C%20but%20stay%20consistent%20with%20the%20time.%20The%20key%20is%20to%20be%20as%20committed%20to%20yourself%20as%20you%20would%20be%20to%20your%20boss%2C%20and%20to%20be%20mindful%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Diya%20Celine%20Simon%20is%20a%20Communications%20Professional%20with%20a%20Bachelor's%20in%20Media%20and%20Communications%2C%20English%20Literature%20and%20Psychology.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689595800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2F2vl2sq2_bengaluru-generic-getty-_625x300_29_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fa-students-guide-to-hustle-culture-and-its-fallout-4215299%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Too%20much%20work%20and%20limited%20play%20could%20lead%20to%20the%20worst%20outcome%20-%20burnout.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%