t%20six%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20--%20one%20more%20than%20his%20uncle%20Pashupati%20Paras%20currently%20has.%20Paswan%20Junior%2C%20who%20has%20been%20isolated%20after%20the%202019%20assembly%20elections%2C%20placed%20his%20demands%20before%20Union%20home%20minister%20and%20the%20BJP's%20chief%20strategist%20Amit%20Shah%20today%2C%20sources%20said.%20While%20the%20BJP%20response%20is%20not%20known%20yet%2C%20the%20party%20has%20been%20pushing%20for%20a%20rapprochement%20between%20the%20two%20factions%20of%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan's%20Lok%20Janashakti%20Party%20--%20currently%20being%20led%20by%20the%20uncle%20and%20nephew.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crucial%20meeting%20with%20Paswan%20Junior%20took%20place%20this%20afternoon%20ahead%20of%20the%20mega%20huddle%20of%20the%20NDA%2C%20due%20on%20July%2018.%20For%20tomorrow's%20meet%2C%20Besides%20Chirag%20Paswan%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20also%20invited%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20Ham%20(Hindustani%20Awam%20Morcha)%20which%20it%20managed%20to%20pry%20loose%20from%20the%20Grand%20Alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20is%20trying%20to%20mop%20up%20multiple%20caste%20groups%20to%20chip%20away%20at%20the%20voter%20base%20of%20the%20Grand%20alliance%20--%20a%20re-unification%20of%20the%20two%20factions%20of%20the%20LJP%20is%20crucial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20six%20per%20cent%20Paswan%20voters%20are%20apparently%20backing%20Chirag%20Paswan%20and%20not%20his%20uncle.%20Without%20their%20support%2C%20the%20formula%20to%20beat%20the%20Maha%20Gathbandhan's%20%26quot%3BLuv-Kush%26quot%3B%20(Kurmi-Koeri)%20and%20%26quot%3BMuslim-Yadav%26quot%3B%20numbers%2C%20is%20bound%20to%20go%20awry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20not%20be%20plain%20sailing%20for%20the%20BJP%20even%20if%20Chirag%20Paswan's%20demands%20are%20met.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20leader%20and%20Union%20minister%20Nityanand%20Rai's%20overtures%20to%20Mr%20Paras%20has%20already%20drawn%20a%20blank.%20Mr%20Paras%2C%20who%20is%20the%20Minister%20of%20Food%20Processing%20Industries%20in%20the%20Central%20government%2C%20is%20angling%20for%20a%20seat%20on%20which%20Chirag%20Paswan%20has%20his%20eye%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20uncle%20and%20nephew%20are%20currently%20caught%20in%20a%20battle%20over%20the%20Hajipur%20seat%20--%20both%20aiming%20to%20claim%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan's%20legacy.%C2%A0%20In%20his%20lifetime%2C%20the%20seat%20was%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan.%20In%202019%2C%20Mr%20Paras%20won%20from%20there%20and%20Chirag%20Paswan%20from%20Jamui.%20Mr%20Paras%20now%20refuses%20to%20give%20up%20the%20seat%20for%20his%20nephew.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20backdrop%2C%20the%20BJP%20request%20for%20unification%20got%20short%20shrift%20from%20Mr%20Paras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Nityanand%20Rai)%20said%20uncle%2C%20nephew%2C%20get%20together%2C%20I%20said%20it%20is%20not%20possible.%20When%20things%20go%20wrong%2C%20when%20the%20milk%20curdles%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20hard%20you%20try%2C%20you%20get%20no%20butter%2C%26quot%3B%20Pashupati%20Paras%20told%20reporters%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20questioned%20his%20nephew's%20claim%20to%20the%20seat.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20is%20that%20when%20your%20father%20was%20alive%2C%20you%20were%20asked%20to%20contest%20from%20Jamui%20and%20not%20from%20Hajipur%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bihar%20chief%20of%20LJP's%20Chirag%20Paswan%20faction%20indicated%20that%20the%20issue%20of%20Hajipur%20could%20have%20been%20settled.%20Describing%20the%20talks%20with%20Mr%20Shah%20as%20'positive%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%2C%20Chirag%20Paswan%20has%20already%20spoken...%20Chirag%20Paswan%20will%20contest%20from%20Hajipur%20seat%26quot%3B.%20Asked%20about%20the%20claims%20of%20Mr%20Paras%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWho%20is%20saying%20what%3F%20We%20don't%20care%20what%20he%20is%20saying%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar's%20move%20to%20break%20away%20from%20the%20NDA%20last%20year%20and%20stitchin