ening%20to%20what%20we%20were%20saying%20and%20after%20meeting%20him%2C%20we%20are%20going%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20Praful%20Patel%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20we%20met%20our%20God%20and%20our%20leader%20Sharad%20Pawar%20to%20take%20his%20blessings%2C%26quot%3B%20Praful%20Patel%20said%20as%20the%20rebels%20emerged%20from%20the%20meeting%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20came%20here%20without%20asking%20for%20any%20appointment.%20We%20understood%20Sharad%20Pawar%20reached%20here%20for%20a%20meeting%20and%20that's%20why%20we%20all%20came%20here%20to%20take%20his%20blessings%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20addressed%20the%20party%20workers%20later%20in%20the%20day%20and%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20he%20will%20continue%20his%20%26quot%3Bprogressive%20politics%26quot%3B%20and%20never%20ally%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCP%20patriarch%2C%2082%2C%20has%20been%20a%20leading%20player%20in%20trying%20to%20unite%20various%20parties%20against%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENCP%20split%20earlier%20this%20month%20when%20Ajit%20Pawar%20left%20the%20Opposition%20ranks%20and%20took%20oath%20as%20the%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Pawar%2C%20who%20claims%20the%20support%20of%20more%20NCP%20MLAs%20than%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20also%20visited%20his%20uncle's%20home%20last%20week%20to%20meet%20with%20his%20aunt%20Pratibha%20Pawar%20--%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20wife%20--%20who%20had%20a%20surgery%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689594600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F3p4qjccs_ait-pawar-sharad-pawar_625x300_17_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fajit-pawar-meets-uncle-sharad-pawar-second-meeting-in-24-hours-4214647%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20wh