%3Cp%3EBritish-French%20actress%C2%A0and%20singer%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fjane-birkin-at-75-pop-icon-par-excellence%2Fa-60095573%5C%22%3EJane%20Birkin%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20passed%20away%C2%A0in%20Paris%20at%20the%20age%20of%2076%2C%20the%20French%20Culture%20Ministry%20said%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20London-born%20entertainer%C2%A0suffered%20from%20health%20problems%20in%20recent%20years%20that%20forced%20her%20to%20cancel%20concerts.%20She%20had%20a%20mild%20stroke%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBirkin%20first%20became%20famous%20internationally%20in%201969%20when%20she%20and%20her%20lover%2C%20the%20late%20French%20musician%20Serge%20Gainsbourg%2C%20sang%20the%20controversial%20hit%20song%20%E2%80%98Je%20T%E2%80%99aime%E2%80%A6%20Moi%20Non%20Plus%E2%80%99%20with%20sexually%20explicit%20lyrics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinding%20love%20in%20Paris%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJane%20Mallory%20Birkin%20was%20born%20in%20London%20in%20December%201946.%20Her%20mother%20was%20an%20actress%20Judy%20Campbell%20and%C2%A0her%20father%20a%20naval%20officer%20David%20Birkin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20first%20marriage%20came%20at%2017%2C%20when%20Birkin%20married%20composer%20John%20Barry%2C%20himself%20famous%20for%20composing%20the%20iconic%20%E2%80%98James%20Bond%E2%80%99%20theme.%20Birkin%20and%20Barry%20had%20a%20daughter%2C%20Kate%2C%20but%20their%20marriage%20fell%20apart%20after%20only%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201966%2C%20Birkin%20appeared%20nude%20in%20Michelangelo%20Antonioni%E2%80%99s%20film%20%3Cem%3EBlow-Up%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20a%20part%20of%20a%20threesome%20sex%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20on%20a%20set%20of%20a%20romantic%20comedy%20in%20Paris%2C%20she%20met%20French%20singer%20and%20songwriter%20Serge%20Gainsbourg.%20Although%C2%A0Gainsbourg%20was%2018%20years%20older%2C%20the%20two%20started%20a%2013-year-long%20relationship%20that%20prompted%20Birkin%20to%20permane