0includes%20plans%20to%20revive%20stalled%20high-level%20climate%20diplomacy%20and%20exert%20pressure%20on%20China%20to%20increase%20efforts%20to%20reduce%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions%2C%20particularly%20as%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Flast-8-years-warmest-on-record-globally-says-eu-report%2Fa-64342613%5C%22%3Erecord-breaking%20heatwaves%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20intensified%20by%20climate%20change%2C%20affect%20various%20regions%20of%20the%20northern%20hemisphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20meeting%20marks%20the%20first%20comprehensive%20face-to-face%20climate%20dialogue%20between%20representatives%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fnew-climate-pledges-to-cut-emissions-still-fall-short%2Fa-57284816%5C%22%3Etwo%20largest%20climate%20polluters%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0after%20nearly%20a%20yearlong%20hiatus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%E2%80%99re%20trying%20to%20do%20is%20find%20ways%20we%20can%20cooperate%20to%20actually%20address%20the%20crisis%E2%80%9D%20of%20climate%2C%20Kerry%20had%20said%20before%20his%20visit%2C%20calling%20China%20critical%20to%20their%20%E2%80%9Cbeing%20able%20to%20solve%20this%20problem.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChina%20central%20to%20global%20efforts%20to%20reduce%20emissions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meeting%2C%20Kerry%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20making%20tangible%20progress%20in%20the%20four%20months%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20COP28%20global%20climate%20talks%20in%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20committed%20to%20reaching%20peak%20carbon%20dioxide%20emissions%20by%202030%20and%20achieving%20carbon%20neutrality%20by%202060.%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20has%20also%20said%20that%20the%20country%20will%20reduce%20its%20use%20of%20coal%20from%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20the%20European%20Union%20have%20urged%20the%20Asian%20powerhouse%20to%20adopt%20more%20ambitious%20emission%20reduction%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%2C%20both%20the%20largest%20producer%20and%20consumer%20of%20coal%2C%20has%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fchina-sandstorms-blanket-beijing-as-air-pollution-spikes%2Fa-65074736%5C%22%3Econtinued%20constructing%20new%20coal%20plants%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0while%20simultaneously%20investing%20in%20renewable%20energy%20sources%20such%20as%20solar%20and%20wind%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerry%20emphasised%20that%20the%20substantial%20gap%20between%20China%E2%80%99s%20claims%20and%20its%20status%20as%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20second-largest%20economy%20should%20not%20hinder%20global%20efforts%20to%20reduce%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Steering%20bilateral%20relations%20back%20on%20track%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20US%20seeks%20to%20reestablish%20communication%20channels%20amidst%20disagreements%20over%20trade%2C%20Taiwan%2C%20human%20rights%2C%20and%20territorial%20claims%2C%20at%20home%2C%20some%20Republicans%20have%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20appropriateness%20of%20engaging%20in%20climate%20negotiations%20with%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20US%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Jake%20Sullivan%20told%20CNN%20that%20China%20bears%20the%20responsibility%20to%20reduce%20emissions%20along%20with%20every%20other%20country%20and%20should%20not%20%E2%80%9Chide%20behind%20any%20kind%20of%20claim%20that%20they%20are%20a%20developing%20nation%E2%80%9D%20in%20order%20to%20slow-roll%20efforts%20to%20cut%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerry%E2%80%99s%20visit%20follows%20recent%20trips%20to%20China%20by%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fyellen-urges-us-and-china-to-cooperate-on-climate-financing%2Fa-66163735%5C%22%3ETreasury%20Secretary%20Janet%20Yellen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20the%20Biden%20administration%20aims%20to%20establish%20stability%20in%20the%20broader%20bilateral%20relationship%20with%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERelations%20between%20the%20two%20giant%20economies%20had%20run%20into%20rough%20waters%20after%20then-House%20Speaker%20Nancy%20Pelosi%E2%80%99s%20trip%20to%20Taiwan%20in%20August%20and%20the%20February%20shooting%20down%20of%20Chinese%20spy%20balloon%2C%20according%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20administration%20seeks%20cooperation%20with%20China%20to%20address%20the%20climate%20crisis%20while%20maintaining%20a%20firm%20stance%20on%20other%20contentious%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%E2%80%99s%20state-run%20Xinhua%20news%20agency%20called%20recent%20US-China%20official%20interactions%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20sign%20for%20preventing%20further%20miscalculations%2C%20and%20steering%20bilateral%20relations%20back%20on%20track%E2%80%9D%20in%20a%20commentary%20published%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fus-china-envoys-hold-climate-crisis-talks-in-beijing%2Fa-66250950%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ftop-stories%2Fs-9097%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689589928000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17160054%2Fimage-1126.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fus-china-envoys-hold-climate-crisis-talks-in-beijing%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US-China%20discussions%20are%20expected%20to%20focus%20on%20addressing%20non-CO2%20emissions%2C%20particularly%20methane%2C%20and%20preparing%20for%20the%20COP28%20summit.%20The%20talks%20come%20amid%20political%20tensions%20between%20the%20two%20nations%20on%20multiple%20fronts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fus-china-envoys-hold-climate-crisis-talks-in-beijing%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Owners%20i