jan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%2C%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20Secular%20and%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%2C%20which%20have%20an%20MP%20each%20in%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20opposition%2C%20105%20members%20are%20against%20the%20Delhi%20Ordinance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20clear%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20test%2C%20the%20government%20will%20need%20help%20from%20the%20BJD%20and%20YSRCP%2C%20which%20have%20nine%20members%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJD%20has%20said%20it%20will%20decide%20when%20the%20bill%20to%20replace%20the%20Delhi%20ordinance%20comes%20up%20for%20discussion%20and%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20YSRCP's%20Jagan%20Reddy%20is%20also%20yet%20to%20reveal%20his%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20both%20parties%20had%20walked%20out%20during%20a%20vote%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20a%20controversial%20bill.%20This%20helped%20the%20government%20by%20bringing%20down%20the%20majority%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20they%20do%20the%20same%20this%20time%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20will%20surpass%20the%20majority%20mark%2C%20which%20will%20have%20dropped%20to%20111.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20will%20be%20in%20trouble%20only%20if%20the%20two%20parties%20vote%20against%20the%20bill%2C%20which%20does%20not%20seem%20likely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20also%20has%20the%20option%20of%20nominating%20two%20members%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20before%20voting%20on%20the%20Delhi%20Ordinance%2C%20increasing%20its%20tally%20to%20114.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fight%20between%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20the%20AAP%20government%20in%20Delhi%20over%20the%20control%20of%20services%20in%20the%20capital%20escalated%20after%20the%20Centre%20passed%20a%20special%20order%20to%20override%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20that%20said%20the%20elected%20government%20in%20Delhi%2C%20not%20the%20Centre%2C%20has%20control%20over%20the%20transfer%20and%20appointments%20of%20bureaucrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20Kejriwa