%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17120524%2Fimage-1124.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20the%20world%20witnessed%20the%20historic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fspace%2Fchandrayaan-3-mission-launch-successful%5C%22%3EChandrayaan-3%20lunar%20mission%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20July%2014%2C%20the%20engineers%20who%20built%20the%20launch%20pad%20are%20reported%20to%20have%20not%20received%20their%20salaries%20for%20over%20a%20year%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20engineers%20of%20Heavy%20Engineering%20Corporation%20(HEC)%20in%20Ranchi%20were%20not%20being%20paid%20for%20the%20past%2017%20months%2C%20news%20agency%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Fviral%2Fchandraayan-3-engineers-who-built-the-launch-pad-completed-work-despite-unpaid-dues-8342071.html%5C%22%3EIANS%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20issue%20of%20unpaid%20salaries%2C%20the%20firm%20delivered%20the%20mobile%20launching%20pad%20and%20other%20crucial%20and%20complex%20equipment%20ahead%20of%20schedule%20in%20December%202022%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20HEC%20is%20a%20public%20sector%20undertaking%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Heavy%20Industries.%20The%20firm%20is%20located%20in%20Ranchi%E2%80%99s%20Dhurwa%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20news%20outlets%20have%20reported%20about%20the%20non-payment%20of%20salaries%20to%20the%20company%20staff%20for%20over%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFrontline%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fthe-nation%2Ffuture-of-hec-hangs-in-the-balance-as-employee-salaries-remain-unpaid-for-over-a-year%2Farticle66838619.ece%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20May%20that%20some%202%2C700%20workmen%20and%20450%20executives%20had%20not%20got%20their%20salaries%20for%20the%20past%2014%20months%20or%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202022%2C%20IANS%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fin.investing.com%2Fnews%2Ffund-crisis-at-hec-3400-officers-workers-not-paid-for-a-year-3410463%5C%22%3Ehad%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20officers%20of%20the%20company%20had%20not%20received%20their%20salary%20for%20an%20entire%20year%20and%20employees%20for%20eight-nine%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20said%20that%20despite%20having%20orders%20worth%20Rs%201%2C500%20crore%20from%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%2C%20Railways%2C%20Coal%20India%20and%20the%20steel%20sector%2C%2080%25%20of%20the%20work%20remains%20pending%20due%20to%20shortage%20of%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubhash%20Chandra%2C%20an%20engineer%20who%20was%20among%20those%20who%20cheered%20the%20successful%20launch%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%2C%20told%20the%20news%20agency%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20HEC%20personnel%20held%20their%20heads%20once%20again%20with%20pride.%20We%20are%20happy%20that%20we%20are%20partners%20in%20such%20an%20important%20project%20of%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIANS%20reported%2C%20citing%20sources%2C%20that%20the%20company%20requested%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Heavy%20Industries%20several%20times%20to%20provide%20working%20capital%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore.%20However%2C%20the%20ministry%20responded%20saying%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20cannot%20extend%20any%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20for%20the%20last%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%2C%20the%20HEC%20has%20not%20made%20any%20permanent%20appointment%20for%20the%20position%20of%20c%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehief%20managing%20director%2C%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3ECMD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chandrayaan-3%20was%20built%20with%20a%20budget%20of%20around%20Rs%20600%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689576083000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17120524%2Fimage-1124.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2