tion%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20I%20was%20very%20happy%20in%20my%20career%2C%20the%20urge%20was%20always%20there.%20However%2C%20when%20we%20were%20home%20because%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20it%20became%20stronger.%20I%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20to%20think.%20This%20is%20when%20I%20started%20to%20question%20whether%20what%20I%20am%20doing%20is%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20social%20divide%20of%20our%20country%20became%20so%20much%20more%20visible.%20I%20started%20to%20ponder%20if%20I%20could%20be%20of%20some%20help%20and%20if%20I%20could%20use%20my%20resources%20to%20make%20things%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20birth%20of%20Aazol%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApurva%20decided%20to%20take%20early%20retirement%20in%202021%20to%20brainstorm%20ideas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20spoke%20to%20my%20son%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20he%20is%20also%20passionate%20about%20helping%20the%20bottom%20tier%20of%20society.%20This%20was%20it%3B%20we%20both%20made%20up%20our%20minds%20to%20find%20a%20way%20of%20helping%20the%20underprivileged%20by%20giving%20them%20a%20livelihood%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20year%2C%20Apurva%20and%20Siddharth%20went%20to%20Mahalaxmi%20Saras%20Exhibition%20which%20happens%20every%20year%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20exhibition%20is%20by%20people%20from%20all%20across%20Maharashtra%20from%20various%20SHGs%20showcasing%20and%20selling%20their%20produce.%20While%20chatting%20with%20these%20women%2C%20I%20realised%20how%20they%20did%20not%20have%20many%20avenues%20to%20sell%20these%20products.%20There%20were%20so%20many%20snacks%20and%20products%20like%20chutney%2C%20sauces%20and%20syrups%20that%20I%20had%20never%20seen%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHaving%20lived%20in%20Maharashtra%20my%20whole%20life%20I%20was%20shocked%