ace%20for%20kids%20to%20spend%20their%20time%20in%20nature%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaurabh%20and%20Akanksha%20have%20pursued%20their%20mission%20of%20sustainable%20architecture%20for%20years.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20our%20projects%20are%20green%20certified.%20One%20of%20our%20earliest%20school%20campuses%20was%20the%20BRCM%20school%20in%20a%20semi-arid%20zone%20of%20Haryana%2C%20constructed%20in%20the%201980s%20and%20built%20around%20sustainable%20ideas%20to%20reuse%20and%20recycle%20water%20to%20create%20a%20green%20oasis%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20desert.%20We%20believe%20that%20sustainable%20development%20is%20important%20for%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Akanksha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Outdoor%20spaces%20to%20learn%20in%20and%20from%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20design%20uses%20the%20vegetation%20and%20natural%20features%20of%20the%20school%20to%20its%20advantage%2C%20with%20trees%20becoming%20the%20focal%20points%20within%20the%20building%E2%80%99s%20design.%20%E2%80%9CNinety%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20trees%20on%20the%20property%20were%20saved%20from%20being%20chopped%20down.%20The%20school%20campus%20moves%20around%20the%20trees%20and%20vegetation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trees%20grow%20throughout%20the%20building%2C%20creating%20transitional%20spaces%20between%20classroom%20clusters%2C%20courtyards%2C%20activity%20zones%2C%20walkways%2C%20and%20congregational%20areas%2C%20providing%20a%20green%20and%20refreshing%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20achieve%20this%2C%20we%20created%20various%20outdoor%20spaces%20for%20the%20students%20to%20learn%20in%20and%20from.%20For%20instance%2C%20we%20have%20outdoor%20classrooms%20to%20encourage%20students%20to%20observe%2C%20learn%20and%20interact%20with%20their%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfig